# AquaVerse

A cozy, first-person aquaculture simulation game built with Unity.

## Setup
- Unity version: 2022.3.x LTS
- Input System: New Input System enabled
- Controls:
  - WASD = Move
  - Mouse = Look
  - E = Interact
  - Tab = Journal

## Features (in progress)
- First-person controller
- Quest system
- Pond management
- Mini-games for feed, harvest, water quality
